org.apache.hadoop.fs

Class CommonConfigurationKeys

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.fs.CommonConfigurationKeysPublic
      • org.apache.hadoop.fs.CommonConfigurationKeys
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FtpConfigKeys, LocalConfigKeys, LocalFileSystemConfigKeys

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
@InterfaceStability.Unstable
public class CommonConfigurationKeys
extends CommonConfigurationKeysPublic
    This class contains constants for configuration keys used in the common code. It inherits all the publicly documented configuration keys and adds unsupported keys.
